{
  "title": "Very Gooey Dutch Turnip Stew",
  "description": "A traditional Dutch dish featuring turnips and nuka-pickle, this stew is perfect for a cold winter night, with a bitter and gooey flavor profile that is egg-free-friendly.",
  "cuisine": "Dutch",
  "diet": [
